Package com.wikischool.wikischool.main.utilities

Class HashMap_FNV<Key,​Value>

java.lang.Object
com.wikischool.wikischool.main.utilities.HashMap_FNV<Key,​Value>
public class HashMap_FNV<Key,​Value>
extends java.lang.Object
Hash Map implementation. Keys are hashed using Fowler-NOLL-Vo hash function Collisions of hashed keys are resolved with separate chaining.
Author:
sean-harnett
